text: Thomas Larsen (born 16 October 1968) is a Danish rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Danish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Denmark Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Holstebro Municipality
